    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Check out this dependable ride that's perfect for anyone looking for a solid value! This car has been a reliable companion and is ready for its next chapter. While it shows some honest character through visible interior and exterior wear, it still runs well and offers a practical, budget-friendly driving experience. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a functional vehicle at a price that leaves plenty of room in your wallet!",
